org.bytedeco.bullet.Bullet3OpenCL

Class b3QuantizedBvh

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
      • org.bytedeco.bullet.Bullet3OpenCL.b3QuantizedBvh
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    b3OptimizedBvh

    @NoOffset
 @Properties(inherit=Bullet3OpenCL.class)
public class b3QuantizedBvh
extends Pointer
    The b3QuantizedBvh class stores an AABB tree that can be quickly traversed on CPU and Cell SPU. It is used by the b3BvhTriangleMeshShape as midphase It is recommended to use quantization for better performance and lower memory requirements.
